---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Manut.dev" description="Hey, I'm Vanilas! A software developer tired of the routine grind and looking to break into game development">
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <section class="text-center py-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        About Me
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Hey, I'm Vanilas! A software developer breaking free from the routine
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-8">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-4">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gray-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-gray-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Vanilas</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Software Developer & Game Dev Enthusiast</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Who I Am</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Hey, I'm Vanilas! I'm a software developer who's pretty damn tired of the routine job grind and looking to break into game development.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">What I'm Into</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            I'm really interested in politics, social issues, world history, and game theory - basically anything related to power dynamics and how systems work. I love digging into the real mechanics of control, influence, and money, not just the bullshit they teach in textbooks.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            I love playing games, especially adult games that push boundaries. Gaming isn't just entertainment - it's a way to explore different realities and experience power dynamics safely. From strategy games to RPGs, I'm here for all of it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">My Creative Side</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            In my routine, I spend a lot of time generating images with Stable Diffusion on my fucking local computer. I train my own LoRA models on them and do hands-on image editing myself. I'm not just some asshole who clicks buttons on AI tools - I actually want to use AI to enhance my skills, not replace them.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">What This Blog Is About</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            I'll mainly be sharing stuff I actually do in real life - like coding projects, random ideas that pop into my head, or thoughts about world politics, fucking trade, money, or life in general.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Keep In Touch</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            If you find what I share interesting or want to chat about similar stuff, stick around. Let's see where this journey goes.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a 
              href="https://github.com/pornmanut" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors"
            >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
              </svg>
              <span>GitHub</span>
            </a>
            <a 
              href="https://linkedin.com/in/pornmanut" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors"
            >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
              </svg>
              <span>LinkedIn</span>
            </a>
            <a 
              href="mailto:contact@manut.dev" 
              class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors"
            >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Email</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
